Ed - Reactive Data Framework for Enu

Ed provides thread-safe, network-synchronized reactive data containers.

Warning: Data consistency is eventual, not guaranteed. Do not use for critical data. Full consistency support planned for future versions.

Basic usage:

import ed

Ed.bootstrap
let name = ed("Enu")
name.track proc(changes: auto) =
  for change in changes:
    echo "Changed: ", change.item
name.value = "World"
